msg":"操你媽<br />\n<br />\n廣東話屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦，垃圾5毛"},{"pid":"476fee318fb6e9f17ceeca12bf325489b46e479d","tid":652653,"uid":167326,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:23:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得用番主語英文其次中文好啲。<br />\n始於英文係世界第一語言"},{"pid":"a74abc81e6adac8518d76515a5c062e0fb48bdc0","tid":652653,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"50年前<br />\n<br />\n潮洲話，福建話<br />\n都輪唔到強國共產黨語言普通話啦"},{"pid":"64861e8d38f9459a835ad818d486e776766d744b","tid":652653,"uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"五十年前講廣東話人口不到一半可能係真，但六十年前、七十年前、八十年前講廣東話既人肯定佔多數，所以五十年前嚟香港嗰班人都要學講廣東話，包括我既長輩"},{"pid":"d81c4ac71971b3f9304e89443bf359cb65765dfc","tid":652653,"uid":2322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"就算係 咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b6440aaa1ba940aa1ba143cf8145cc98229835","tid":652653,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/132819_dfbde4c9cac6a818c601a8c36c832458.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F132819_dfbde4c9cac6a818c601a8c36c832458.png&h=c3f133bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/132822_92963e5744278739ee00a84f5dca4d6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F132822_92963e5744278739ee00a84f5dca4d6e.png&h=8f5e4ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/132825_51f3f1b4da56718787d4f460f59a2bbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F132825_51f3f1b4da56718787d4f460f59a2bbe.png&h=20e2871d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79f44598f8d83f6a7cc